      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><ol>
<li>登录FCoin账户</li>
<li>依次点击【设置】--【安全设置】--【绑定】<img src="/hc/article_attachments/360022082173/_____1.png" alt="_____1.png"></li>
<li>选择您所在的国家，并输入手机号，点击【下一步】<img src="/hc/article_attachments/360022082213/_____2.png" alt="_____2.png"></li>
<li>拖动滑块完成拼图</li>
</ol>
<p>       <img src="/hc/article_attachments/360022082233/_____3.png" alt="_____3.png"></p>
<p> 5.  系统将向您发送短信验证码，请输入验证码，并点击【确定】，完成手机号的绑定。</p>
<p>      <img src="/hc/article_attachments/360021155614/_____4.png" alt="_____4.png"></p></div>

